OL,3,CCouncil U-turns on decision not to
OL,4,Cdisplay Hanukkah candles following
OL,5,Cbacklash
OL,7,FHavering Council has reversed its
OL,8,Fdecision not to display Hanukkah
OL,9,Fcandles this year in a bid to avoid
OL,10,F"inflaming community tensions".
OL,12,FThe east London borough announced the
OL,13,Fmove yesterday due to concerns the
OL,14,Fmenorah - a nine-branched candelabrum
OL,15,Flit during the eight-day Jewish
OL,16,Fholiday - would be vandalised.
OL,18,FIt came amid a surge in antisemitic
OL,19,Fhate crimes in the capital following
OL,20,FIsrael's war with Hamas in Gaza.
